1. Build FENRIR for desired system architecture
2. Copy FENRIR zip into fenrir folder
3. cd FENRIR && tar -cf FENRIR_1.0.0.tar FENRIR_1.0.0
4. ssh-keygen -f '/home/localadmin/.ssh/known_hosts' -R 'fenrir.local'
5. cd .. && scp FENRIR/FENRIR_1.0.0.tar localadmin@fenrir.local:/home/localadmin
6. ssh localadmin@fenrir.local 
7. tar -xsvf FENRIR_1.0.0.tar
8. chmod +x FENRIR_1.0.0/install/installer.sh
9. ./FENRIR_1.0.0/install/installer.sh
10. Connect to Fenrir access point
11. http://10.42.0.1:8000/fenrir/web

